{"tid":2296111,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台美扑槌經濟合作 半導體戰略優先","createTime":"2020-11-22T08:29:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T08:31:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2ad965340df471b38fb7c9db10f2eefed7425e13","tid":2296111,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T08:29:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201122/JBRYAYVPVFHVFMYXZKV6UFPGZA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201122%2FJBRYAYVPVFHVFMYXZKV6UFPGZA%2F&d=icC9UeWzMg70WCHWfTItT0PYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=0b2a52d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201122%2FJBRYAYVPVFHVFMYXZKV6UFPGZA%2F&h=6f4e33e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201122/JBRYAYVPVFHVFMYXZKV6UFPGZA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n台美扑槌經濟合作 半導體戰略優先<br />\n<br />\n美國環境保護局局長惠勒訪台前夕，......................。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：連續兩日與特朗普「同台」  G20拍板助窮國 習推國際健康碼<br />\n<br />\n台美首次「經濟繁榮夥伴對話（EPP）」美國時間周五在華府舉行，會中雙方簽署備忘錄，由台灣駐美代表蕭美琴及美國在台協會（AIT）執行理事藍鶯代表簽署。隨後，台美在台北共同舉行記者會，公佈對話九項事實清單。雙方就經濟最高層級的對話機制，預計每年召開，輪流在華府與台北舉辦，不因政黨輪替而受影響。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/U2-Ufu2vxG5g4f_JFFgf8J1Ei14=/640x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/O7TAYHJOWRBRPOHA5ZDTOO2DAU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FU2-Ufu2vxG5g4f_JFFgf8J1Ei14%3D%2F640x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FO7TAYHJOWRBRPOHA5ZDTOO2DAU.jpg&h=293bed8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■台灣外交部長吳釗燮（左）、美國在台協會台北辦事處處長酈英傑（左二）等在記者會合照。台灣蘋果新聞網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政黨輪替不影響對話<br />\n<br />\n另外，台美認為台灣高科技硬體製造具競爭優勢，雙方確認在半導體領域的戰略合作為優先項目。美方還主動提出，簽署備忘錄的效期達五年，在美國政權即將輪替之際，為台灣打強心針。經濟合作領域方面，雙方明確未來透過對話建立工作小組處理經濟議題，印太地區是焦點區域之一。健康安全方面，雙方尋求數碼科技研發合作，確保兩地醫療物資及服務自由流通。5G及電信安全方面，美國確定台灣是5G乾淨通道夥伴。雙方還提到婦女經濟賦權、基礎建設及投資審查等雙方合作。<br />\n<br />\n總統蔡英文昨在fb發文強調，................................<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網"},{"pid":"5e82253209cb6270d14ddb7390700a290c0747d1","tid":2296111,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T08:29:47.000Z","msg":"中共：我會炸9台灣"},{"pid":"271f8c3af7525f99a7f1b7290a6eae7375a28b2c","tid":2296111,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T08:30:17.000Z","msg":"大和田.gif <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83af623d22a38be818882c178b3cb304cc0928e7","tid":2296111,"uid":54552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T08:31:35.000Z","msg":"中央：台灣是中国的 要談先和我談<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}